. A list of topics are included in the slides\nattached.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are also taking this opportunity to officially launch the new\n'HRS Science Revision Site', which is designed as your place to go\nfor all the revision resources you need. You can find on there:</p>\n<p>- Revision checklists, knowledge organisers, revision mats for\neach topic</p>\n<p>- Required practical info</p>\n<p>- Information on recommended revision guides</p>\n<p>- Links to past papers</p>\n<p>- Useful tips on how to revise science</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You will be able to access the site when you are logged in to\nyour school google account. The link to the site is:&nbsp;<a href=\n\"https://sites.google.com/hrs.education/hrs-science-revision/\"\ntarget=\n\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/hrs.education/hrs-science-revision/</a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>If you have any questions at all or want some more guidance on\nhow or what to revise, then please get in touch with your science\nteacher or come and see us in the office any time.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Happy revising!</p>\n<p>Dr Evans</p>\n\n","issue_date":"2024-10-04","due_date":"2024-11-04","completion_time_unit":"minutes","completion_time_value":"","publish_time":"00:00:00","status":{"id":517384624,"state":null,"mark":null,"mark_relative":0,"ticked":"no","allow_attachments":false,"allow_marking_completed":true,"first_seen_date":"2024-10-14T18:59:37+00:00","last_seen_date":"2024-10-14T18:59:37+00:00","attachments":[],"has_feedback":false},"validated_links":[],"validated_attachments":[{"id":12114853,"filename":"Y11 Nov mocks.pdf","file":"https://attachments.classcharts.com/h/186510/856dbe6c1c41e272821b0779a60a6616_20241003_191841.pdf?GoogleAccessId=attachments-classcharts%40edukey-classcharts.iam.gserviceaccount.com&Expires=1729698368&Signature=bhxA1Efgc7HT%2FB0%2BoWyAxUGE0LkWNiZ8lEnhEtY4ZpzW6yfTfTnN6U7H2%2F3c3h1piAyX9cZF8FRsMLYq2WOo7x2%2FXXXiTUv3CY7TdjRkeUWAHqajCU%2FUR8G%2B64HYVqaxbvRFnrsu2nKrKITX%2FJOjLViPMqrf8PJtk